  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Barista (Coffee and Matcha)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Barista (Coffee and Matcha)</strong></p><p>If you are a dynamic and motivated person who has strong interpersonal skills and more importantly, believe that YOU CAN MAKE A DIFFERENCE to the company, we would like to hear from you.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>Prepare and serve espresso, matcha and specialty beverages</p><p>Provide excellent customer service with a warm and friendly attitude</p><p>Maintain cleanliness and organisation of bar and work area</p><p>Assist with inventory, restocking and daily operations</p><p>Adhere to all health and safety guidelines</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><p>Prior experience as a barista is an advantage</p><p>Knowledge of espresso extraction, milk steaming and matcha whisking techniques</p><p>Positive attitude, team player and good communication skills</p><p>Able to work on rotating shifts and on a 5 days week basis inclusive of weekends and public </p><p>holidays</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><p>Basic + Allowances + Medical benefits + FREE movies!</p><p>Attractive bonuses (applies to full-timers only).</p><p>Career advancement opportunities.</p><p>FUN and LIVELY working environment.</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Interested candidates please e-mail your cover letter and detailed resume with Passport Size Photograph and Indication</p><p>of Expected Salary & Date of Availability to:</p><p>The Recruitment Officer</p><p>Re: Application for the post of Head Chef Recruitment</p><p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:recruitment@shaw.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">recruitment@shaw.com.sg</a></p><p>(Only shortlisted candidates will be notified)</p>",
